    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather and trim appearing as if they just left the factory. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle that presents as brand new.",
