      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been really well-cared for over the years. Whether you're headed to work or hitting the road for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s super clean and looking for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
