    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the torque load without fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile gear selection, sending power through a factory M-variable differential lock. Suspension dynamics are sharp, featuring refreshed control arm bushings and a precise steering rack. While the exterior displays honest road wear, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a linear power band.",
