    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a reliable and well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between utility and comfort. The exterior retains a deep shine, though a close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with typical daily use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and meticulously kept; the leather seats show light bolster wear but remain firm and supportive, and all electronics\u2014including the high-fidelity sound system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and a comprehensive brake service performed last season. The tires currently hold approximately 60% tread, ensuring many miles of worry-free driving before replacement is necessary. This is a solid, honest car that has been a dependable companion and is ready for its next chapter.",
